Think of raw data as a giant pile of receipts.
A materialized view is like keeping a â€œtotal sales by dayâ€ spreadsheet updated automatically.
A data cube is like keeping multiple spreadsheets â€” one for sales by day/product/store/etc. â€” so you can answer common questions instantly.

